reviewText: The start of a great arc. Two recap episodes
Great show this set is ok was a little peeved that the first 4 episodes are annoying and useless recap fillers before it got back to the main story
Funimation has gone a long way with this property! Expecting great things to come.
What else can I say? If you love One Piece then you want this.
This series continues to pull me in. I love the story soooo much, and it never disappoints.
Awesome stuff great anime and manga!
This is a really great collection of episodes. The build up to Whitebeard was amazing.
Great series, cant wait for the rest.
